==English==

===Adjective===
'''permanent''', '''more permanent''', '''most permanent'''

# Without end, [[eternal]].
#: ''Nothing in this world is truly permanent.''
# Lasting for an indefinitely long time.
#: ''The countries are now locked in a permanent state of conflict.''

